HEADWORD: Chimney-breast
<hw>Chim"ney-breast`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Arch.)</fld>
<def>The horizontal projection of a chimney from the wall in which it is
built; -- commonly applied to its projection in the inside of a building
only.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

